meta-llama.description: Llama family including Code Llama, Guard

mistral.description: Direct API access to Mistral models

special_suffixes.:free: Free tier variant with rate limits

lookup_strategy: 1. Check if model has platform prefix (openrouter: or togetherai:)
2. If prefixed, extract company from path (e.g., 'anthropic' from 'openrouter:anthropic/claude-opus-4.5')
3. If Direct model (no prefix), lookup in model_registry by iterating companies
4. If not found in registry, use company_patterns regex matching
